          </div>
          <div class="faq-item">
            <button class="faq-q" onclick="toggleFaq(this)">
              <span class="faq-q-text">Do local justifications affect rankings?</span>
              <span class="faq-toggle"><svg viewBox="0 0 12 12"><path d="M6 1v10M1 6h10" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"/></svg></span>
            </button>
            <div class="faq-a"><div class="faq-a-inner"><p>Local justifications do not directly cause higher rankings — they are a byproduct of Google having sufficient high-quality data about a business to explain its relevance. However, the factors that produce justifications (complete GBP, keyword-rich reviews, structured website data) are the same factors that improve local rankings.</p></div></div>
          </div>
          <div class="faq-item">
            <button class="faq-q" onclick="toggleFaq(this)">
              <span class="faq-q-text">How do I get local justifications for my business?</span>
              <span class="faq-toggle"><svg viewBox="0 0 12 12"><path d="M6 1v10M1 6h10" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"/></svg></span>
            </button>
            <div class="faq-a"><div class="faq-a-inner"><p>Earn justifications by: keeping your GBP services and products fully described with specific keywords, encouraging reviewers to mention services by name in their reviews, ensuring your website includes detailed service descriptions that Google can crawl, and maintaining accurate GBP attributes.</p></div></div>
          </div>
          <div class="faq-item">
            <button class="faq-q" onclick="toggleFaq(this)">
