            </button>
            <div class="faq-a"><div class="faq-a-inner"><p>Google shows several types: review justifications (snippets from customer reviews), website mention justifications (from your website copy), services justifications (from GBP services data), menu justifications (for food businesses), product justifications (from GBP products or LIA feeds), and post justifications (from recent GBP updates).</p></div></div>
          </div>
          <div class="faq-item">
            <button class="faq-q" onclick="toggleFaq(this)">
              <span class="faq-q-text">Can I control what local justifications Google shows?</span>
